data.description: Welcome to Nagy Hill. Charming two-story home in a peaceful neighborhood. A great location within the Klein School District near Grand Parkway. Extremely well maintained move-in-ready. Features 3 beds, 2.5 baths, Open kitchen with breakfast nook and spacious walk-in pantry. Upstairs, you will find a generous sized game room perfect for a pool table. A oversized primary bedroom with flex space that could be used as a nursery, home office, or a sitting area. Primary bedroom offers dual walk in closets and bathroom that boasts of dual vanity sinks and luxurious jetted tub with tiled shower. Enjoy the spacious back yard, with a covered patio, and plenty of room to entertain.
